Yaoyuan de Ai (Far-Away Love) 1947, Chen Liting. 

Yi jiang chunshui xiang dong liu (A Spring River Flows East), 1947, Cai Shusheng Long. 

A dramatic account of the horrors of the Japanese invasion.  

Baqian li lu yun he yue (Eight Thousand Miles of Clouds and Moon), 1946. 


